channel.title: Home teleport (blankscape)
channel.description:
Okay, I wanted to start fresh and test my coding skills. Which didn't take long for me to get stuck on it, I looking up a tutorial on how to make a home teleport spell. I have Texthandler.java but no Clickingmost.java. I'm using Blankscape.
http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=407757.0
I followed this tutorial.
http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/tutorials/259136-pi-teleport-names-adding-descriptions.html
If anyone could redirect me to a different tutorial that will work for this source that would be great! :D If not can someone tell me what I might of did wrong? I'm not asking to be spoon-fed or anything, I really want to code my offline source by myself but a little help would be nice. :P
